<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.5">
<l>tītil naṉṉeṟi niṟkaval lātucey</l>
<l>nīti yāroṭuṅ kūṭuva tillaiyāṉ</l>
<l>āti yāya ṉaraṅkaṉan tāmaraip</l>
<l>pētai māmaṇa vāḷaṉṟaṉ pittaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no associating, for me, with those whose law is doing otherwise</l>
<l rend="indent">while there exists a good path with no vice.</l>
<l>[I am] the madman of the Primal One, the Cowherd, Raṅga,</l>
<l rend="indent">the Husband of the woman Lakṣmī on the beautiful lotus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
